item.title: What one of these is str
item.dc:creator: @chassy13 Chassy13
item.description:
@chassy13 wrote:

Just make the XP so it is 99. Damage calculation is dealt with whatever the top number is set as. You can set your strength even higher as long as it doesn’t move the next set of numbers over in the text file.

item.title: What one of these is str
item.dc:creator: @chassy13 Chassy13
item.description:
@chassy13 wrote:

character-skill = 2, change the 1 to 9999 and then the other number is the XP. Make sure it’s above 13,034,431 or it won’t be 99 (it’s for the number that’s underneath the bar on the skill square).
